1
00:00:01,170 --> 00:00:03,320
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:03,320 --> 00:00:06,250
Wendy and Carla joined our guild,

3
00:00:06,250 --> 00:00:08,280
and things have gotten lively again!

4
00:00:08,280 --> 00:00:11,460
Gildarts came back, too... I'm all fired up!

5
00:00:11,460 --> 00:00:14,630
There's one thing that I 
wonder about, though...

6
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:17,490
There's Mystogan too, right? What is he...

7
00:00:17,490 --> 00:00:18,540
Whoops, time's up!

8
00:00:18,540 --> 00:00:19,990
Let's get a move on!

9
00:01:58,630 --> 00:01:59,730
This isn't it!

10
00:02:00,970 --> 00:02:02,050
Neither is this one!

11
00:02:02,990 --> 00:02:04,220
Or this one!

12
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:19,500
Salamander and that new brat both have one...

13
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:24,240
So why am I the only Dragon 
Slayer without a cat!?

14
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,440
Earthland!

15
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:51,120
Do you still have any figures of Gajeel left?

16
00:02:51,450 --> 00:02:53,380
Oh, you must be a real hard-core fan...

17
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:56,310
Yes, we have some, most definitely...

18
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:00,870
It's even got a stand for 
the cat, just in case!

19
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:02,720
Whoa! Totally gnarly!

20
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:06,560
Well, we designed it with 
the future in mind, see...

21
00:03:11,390 --> 00:03:14,250
Hey, hey! It's only noon, 
would you pipe down?

22
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:18,500
You're one to talk, when you're 
already drinking at noon...

23
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:21,580
Seriously, man... God knows what 
you're doing to your stomach...

24
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:23,220
Shut it, you!

25
00:03:23,220 --> 00:03:26,390
<i>I'm</i> not bothering anyone, am I?

26
00:03:26,390 --> 00:03:28,130
W-We're sorry...

27
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,560
This is difficult...

28
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:35,700
What are you reading?

29
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:39,100
A book of poetry written in ancient Harukan.

30
00:03:39,100 --> 00:03:43,570
Ancient Harukan... Do you mean it's 
written in some ancient language?

31
00:03:44,130 --> 00:03:46,700
That's right. What about it?

32
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,950
Levy, you're so awesome!

33
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:52,460
July 7th, 777...

34
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:56,850
The dragons that taught Natsu-san 
and me Dragon Slayer magic

35
00:03:56,850 --> 00:03:58,920
both disappeared on the same day.

36
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:00,300
Now that you mention it,

37
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:05,300
Natsu might have mentioned that Gajeel's 
dragon vanished the same day, too.

38
00:04:05,850 --> 00:04:07,430
What does it mean?

39
00:04:08,170 --> 00:04:10,150
Maybe they all went camping?

40
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:13,940
Lucy-san, you say some 
strange things sometimes...

41
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:17,900
All set...

42
00:04:18,370 --> 00:04:23,400
The Fire Dragon Igneel, the Iron Dragon 
Metalicana, and the Sky Dragon Grandine...

43
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:27,320
I wonder where they all are now?

44
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:30,330
Aye!

45
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:32,910
Carla!

46
00:04:34,350 --> 00:04:37,180
This is a fish I caught!

47
00:04:37,180 --> 00:04:39,270
I was thinking I could 
give it to you, Carla...

48
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,680
I don't want it.

49
00:04:41,090 --> 00:04:43,670
I hate fish.

50
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:46,720
I see... Then, what do you 
like? Next time, I'll...

51
00:04:46,970 --> 00:04:47,860
Be quiet!

52
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:51,130
Stop hanging around me!

53
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,040
Hey, Carla...

54
00:04:57,450 --> 00:04:59,930
You didn't have to go that far...

55
00:05:00,490 --> 00:05:01,950
Right, Happy?

56
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:07,070
Carla! Don't you think that was mean?

57
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:11,600
Happy, yeah, right... 
What's happy about this?

58
00:05:12,110 --> 00:05:13,880
He doesn't know a damn thing!

59
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:18,330
Wait, Carla!

60
00:05:20,650 --> 00:05:24,790
Don't you think Carla is oddly cold to Happy?

61
00:05:25,460 --> 00:05:27,050
I wonder why...

62
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,390
Carla!

63
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:33,350
What? I thought I told you 
to stop hanging around me.

64
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:39,440
Did I, maybe, do something wrong to you?

65
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,220
No, that's not it...

66
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:47,760
You can't protect Natsu.

67
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:07,150
I will protect Wendy.

68
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:14,510
No matter what happens, I 
will protect Wendy, I swear!

69
00:06:18,290 --> 00:06:20,610
I can protect Natsu, too!

70
00:06:20,610 --> 00:06:23,530
Natsu calls me his partner!

71
00:06:26,570 --> 00:06:27,920
No, you can't.

72
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:34,820
A cat who doesn't even know 
what he is, like you...

73
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:44,460
What... I am?

74
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:53,390
What's with the scratches?

75
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:54,300
Shut yer trap!

76
00:07:09,050 --> 00:07:11,000
Carla!

77
00:07:13,770 --> 00:07:15,220
Carla!

78
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:16,530
Where are you?

79
00:07:21,650 --> 00:07:23,940
Carla, I finally found you.

80
00:07:23,940 --> 00:07:24,790
Wendy...

81
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:28,270
You'll catch a cold without 
an umbrella like that.

82
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:30,550
So will you, Carla.

83
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:39,200
Carla, it hasn't been that long 
since we joined this guild,

84
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:42,330
so I think you have to try and 
get along more with everyone.

85
00:07:42,330 --> 00:07:43,900
There's no need.

86
00:07:45,890 --> 00:07:48,360
As long as you're here, that's enough for me.

87
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:51,280
Why do you always have to be this way?

88
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,140
Who's that?

89
00:08:00,810 --> 00:08:01,750
Wendy...

90
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,620
That voice...

91
00:08:06,450 --> 00:08:09,040
I never would have thought 
you would come to this guild.

92
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:15,550
Jellal!

93
00:08:18,770 --> 00:08:22,080
W-What's the meaning of this? 
I thought you were captured!

94
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:24,630
That was a different person than me.

95
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:25,640
But...

96
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,940
I mean, you're clearly Jellal!

97
00:08:28,410 --> 00:08:31,570
I am Mystogan, a member of Fairy Tail.

98
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:34,530
Seven years ago...

99
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:42,140
While I knew hardly anything about this 
world, I gave my name to you as Jellal...

100
00:08:44,710 --> 00:08:46,050
This world?

101
00:08:47,070 --> 00:08:48,420
You don't mean...

102
00:09:04,130 --> 00:09:06,390
You're the one from seven years ago?

103
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:09,430
You're the Jellal from back then?

104
00:09:11,130 --> 00:09:12,280
I...

105
00:09:13,430 --> 00:09:15,640
I've missed you so much!

106
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:20,670
I'm sorry I wasn't able to see you.

107
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:29,580
But... Now is not the time 
for happy reunions...

108
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:32,870
Without delay...

109
00:09:36,830 --> 00:09:39,050
Get away from this city, without delay!

110
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:42,180
Jellal!

111
00:09:44,460 --> 00:09:46,650
I have failed in my mission...

112
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:53,330
Anima!

113
00:09:53,330 --> 00:09:54,310
What?

114
00:09:54,310 --> 00:09:55,390
What's wrong?

115
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:57,650
No! I'm coming with you!

116
00:09:57,650 --> 00:09:59,860
You can't. It'll be 
dangerous to come with me.

117
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:13,750
Anima has grown too large for 
my power alone to suppress it!

118
00:10:18,170 --> 00:10:21,740
Before long, Magnolia will be wiped out...

119
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:40,020
W-What do you mean?

120
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:42,200
I don't know what you're saying at all!

121
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:46,490
It's over. The destruction 
is already certain...

122
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:50,560
At the very least, you could...

123
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:51,870
What about Fairy Tail?

124
00:10:53,930 --> 00:10:56,210
What about everyone in the guild?

125
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:02,210
This rain just isn't stopping...

126
00:11:02,210 --> 00:11:03,320
You know?

127
00:11:04,610 --> 00:11:06,900
I do not think it is Juvia's fault.

128
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:09,100
Nobody was blaming you.

129
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:12,940
How long are you gonna sleep, Natsu?

130
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,610
Let's scribble on his face!

131
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:31,000
Tell me! What about everyone in the guild?

132
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:35,490
I'm saying that everyone will die!

133
00:11:38,850 --> 00:11:39,510
Wendy!

134
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:42,360
I have to warn everyone!

135
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:45,790
You can't go! You, at least, 
should leave the city!

136
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:48,040
By myself? I could never think of it!

137
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:53,100
Because I'm a member of Fairy Tail now!

138
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:03,610
Gray, please stop these 
kinds of childish pranks.

139
00:12:03,610 --> 00:12:06,070
Who're you callin' a child, eh?

140
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:10,070
Now you're even worse than a kid!

141
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:13,910
Is there a fight?!

142
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:15,530
Let me in on it!

143
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,600
What are you muttering about?

144
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:24,920
A Man! You people need to be more 
assertive! And you call yourself a Man?

145
00:12:26,250 --> 00:12:27,300
Here.

146
00:12:29,260 --> 00:12:32,220
Who drew this on me?

147
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:35,980
There's only one other person 
who'd stoop to your level, right?

148
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,930
Was it you, Gray?

149
00:12:37,930 --> 00:12:39,470
You wanna go, bud?

150
00:12:39,470 --> 00:12:42,680
I punished you for your 
loud-ass snoring, is what!

151
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:44,850
You bastard!

152
00:12:48,700 --> 00:12:52,670
Gray-sama... You look so 
dreamy when you're fighting!

153
00:12:53,310 --> 00:12:56,030
Rainy days are perfect for going 
on dates with your boyfriend...

154
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:59,920
Cana, make sure to leave enough of your 
"boyfriend" to serve guests, okay?

155
00:13:00,210 --> 00:13:03,460
Oh? Where are you going 
on a day like this, Mira?

156
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:05,880
Just to the church...

157
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:09,960
If you're a Man, then get stronger!

158
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:12,010
You won't be able to protect Levy like that!

159
00:13:12,010 --> 00:13:13,260
Y-Yeah...

160
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:14,860
We know.

161
00:13:14,860 --> 00:13:16,830
Elfman, we're leaving!

162
00:13:16,830 --> 00:13:19,080
You tell 'em too, Neechan!

163
00:13:19,450 --> 00:13:22,750
They totally screwed up on their last job.

164
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:27,460
They got knocked out first, and Levy had 
to finish up the job all by herself!

165
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,120
It hurts to hear about it.

166
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,200
We suck so bad...

167
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:34,870
I think Jet and Droy were doing their best.

168
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:37,960
Mira-chan!

169
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,170
...such as it is.

170
00:13:39,170 --> 00:13:40,330
Ouch!

171
00:13:47,770 --> 00:13:48,780
Perhaps...

172
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,780
...if I could at least save Wendy...

173
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,180
I wonder.

174
00:14:06,530 --> 00:14:10,770
Why are Mira-san and Elfman going 
to the church on a day like today?

175
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:12,620
Oh, right.

176
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:16,190
It's almost the anniversary 
of Lisanna's death.

177
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:17,820
Lisanna?

178
00:14:17,820 --> 00:14:20,000
Mira and Elfman's little sister.

179
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:23,770
It was two years ago... An accident on a job.

180
00:14:24,490 --> 00:14:29,040
When it gets close to the anniversary, 
those two start start going to the church.

181
00:14:31,030 --> 00:14:32,870
I see...

182
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:37,300
Now that you mention it, you 
remind me a bit of Lisanna.

183
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,570
I do?

184
00:14:38,570 --> 00:14:40,600
Like how you get along well with Natsu...

185
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:50,480
Damn it... That guy's got too much energy...

186
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,320
Asleep already!?

187
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:58,700
So Natsu used to have a girl, huh?

188
00:15:03,070 --> 00:15:06,100
You're way too sticky.

189
00:15:07,130 --> 00:15:09,590
Can't you eat it without 
getting it everywhere?

190
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:12,970
This is the first time Juvia has eaten it.

191
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:15,050
There they go again...

192
00:15:15,290 --> 00:15:17,640
You eat a caramelized frank like this.

193
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:20,440
You open your mouth really wide and then...

194
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:25,870
It ain't so high class food, you know!

195
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:29,320
Although, it's probably best not to strip.

196
00:15:29,710 --> 00:15:32,140
How can they be so bold?

197
00:15:32,140 --> 00:15:34,070
One day, Bisca and I...

198
00:15:35,930 --> 00:15:38,140
The rain just isn't stopping, is it?

199
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:40,120
Y-Yeah...

200
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:43,040
Looks like you two are as friendly as ever.

201
00:15:43,660 --> 00:15:44,650
We are?

202
00:15:44,650 --> 00:15:45,580
Erza-san...

203
00:15:46,260 --> 00:15:48,230
Cherish this time.

204
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,550
So you don't have any regrets...

205
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:55,590
Hey, Erza! Come over here.

206
00:15:55,590 --> 00:15:56,850
Yes, Master?

207
00:15:57,600 --> 00:16:00,850
It's about that 100-year quest...

208
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:03,490
I've been looking into it, and...

209
00:16:04,100 --> 00:16:06,440
I was thinking of giving it to someone else.

210
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:08,540
Any objections?

211
00:16:08,800 --> 00:16:10,440
I think it's appropriate.

212
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:13,450
Ah, there's nothing to do...

213
00:16:13,450 --> 00:16:16,450
With it raining like this, it's hard 
to get motivated to go on a job.

214
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:21,660
I wish something interesting would happen...

215
00:17:21,830 --> 00:17:23,100
Anima is...

216
00:17:30,620 --> 00:17:33,980
Everyone, we have trouble! The sky...

217
00:17:43,230 --> 00:17:45,360
What is this? Everyone!

218
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:49,340
No way...

219
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:53,880
The guild has... vanished...

220
00:18:55,060 --> 00:18:57,620
And the entire city, too...

221
00:18:57,620 --> 00:18:58,610
It can't be!

222
00:18:59,710 --> 00:19:02,310
What in the world has happened?

223
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,280
Is anyone there?

224
00:19:07,230 --> 00:19:08,870
Anyone?!

225
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:17,800
Anyone...?

226
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:22,220
Huh? Why?

227
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:26,180
Why am I the only one here?

228
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:31,100
Even though the city and 
guild are all gone...

229
00:19:32,650 --> 00:19:34,390
Why am I the only one?

230
00:19:43,930 --> 00:19:46,120
W-What?

231
00:19:46,430 --> 00:19:47,560
Natsu-san!

232
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:48,600
Oh, Wendy...

233
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:51,120
Huh? Where are we?

234
00:19:52,370 --> 00:19:55,370
There was someone left other than me...

235
00:19:55,630 --> 00:19:58,000
You don't remember anything?

236
00:19:59,310 --> 00:20:00,460
Well, I was asleep.

237
00:20:02,130 --> 00:20:04,240
This is the guild.

238
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:04,930
Hah?!

239
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:11,350
A hole suddenly appeared in the sky 
and sucked up the guild and the city!

240
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:17,200
I'm telling the truth! It looks 
like we're the only ones left.

241
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:22,700
Wendy, did you bump your head 
or something? That's nuts...

242
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:24,100
No!

243
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:28,200
Maybe it's only Dragon Slayers that are left?

244
00:20:28,970 --> 00:20:30,030
That's right.

245
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:33,120
Carla!

246
00:20:33,120 --> 00:20:35,920
Thank goodness, you're safe...

247
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:37,040
I guess so.

248
00:20:37,560 --> 00:20:41,310
You should thank the special magic 
power you have as a Dragon Slayer.

249
00:20:42,150 --> 00:20:45,090
I'm glad that at least you two are safe.

250
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:46,930
Carla...

251
00:20:47,340 --> 00:20:49,480
That ain't gonna cut it.

252
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:50,850
It's like you don't give 
a crap about the rest...

253
00:20:50,850 --> 00:20:53,510
Wait... They're really gone?!

254
00:20:54,030 --> 00:20:54,830
Yeah...

255
00:20:55,730 --> 00:20:58,400
Hey, everyone!

256
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:00,820
They're gone. Or, more precisely...

257
00:21:01,470 --> 00:21:04,080
They've been sucked into Anima and wiped out.

258
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:06,610
Anima?

259
00:21:08,050 --> 00:21:09,030
Anima?!

260
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:11,630
The hole in the sky from before.

261
00:21:11,630 --> 00:21:15,960
It's the gate to Edolas, the 
world on the other side.

262
00:21:16,340 --> 00:21:17,580
Edolas?

263
00:21:18,020 --> 00:21:20,920
Hey, you! What the hell have you been saying?

264
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,000
Where is everyone?

265
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:22,920
Natsu-san!

266
00:21:23,380 --> 00:21:26,520
So, Carla... Do you know anything?

267
00:21:26,520 --> 00:21:29,090
And wait, why are you okay, Carla?

268
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:33,080
Natsu!

269
00:21:33,080 --> 00:21:34,810
What is this?

270
00:21:34,810 --> 00:21:36,920
The city...!

271
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:37,880
Happy!

272
00:21:38,180 --> 00:21:39,810
You're safe, I see.

273
00:21:40,410 --> 00:21:44,480
I've come from the other world, Edolas.

274
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:49,240
And so has that he-cat over there.

275
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:53,950
What does this mean?

276
00:22:05,820 --> 00:22:07,750
The reason this city disappeared...

277
00:22:09,390 --> 00:22:11,900
...is because of the he-cat and myself.

278
00:23:55,950 --> 00:24:00,680
Natsu, have you heard there's another 
world that resembles this one?

279
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:03,290
It's one of those things, 
you know... A parasol world.

280
00:24:03,290 --> 00:24:05,830
I think you mean "parallel world".

281
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:11,250
I've heard it's a world that's kind of 
like ours, but with some differences...

282
00:24:11,250 --> 00:24:13,510
So, what about this something-or-other world?

283
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:16,510
Next time: Edolas.

284
00:24:17,060 --> 00:24:21,230
I was thinking, maybe in 
that world I'm a king!

285
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:24,260
If you're a king, Happy, then I'd be a god!

286
00:24:24,260 --> 00:24:26,490


